  "analysis": "The image_editing skill directory doesn't provide direct tools, but I can use the convert command from ImageMagick to convert images to grayscale. I'll install ImageMagick if it's not already installed, then convert each keyframe to grayscale.",
  "plan": "First, I'll check if ImageMagick is installed. If not, I'll install it. Then I'll use the convert command to convert each keyframe to grayscale in-place.",
